<title>USA: Pitney Bowes names new CFO.</title>
<headline>Pitney Bowes names new CFO.</headline>
<dateline>STAMFORD, Conn. 1996-10-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Pitney Bowes Inc said Tuesday it had named Murray Reichenstein as vice president and chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Reichenstein replaces Carmine Adimando, who previously announced he was leaving the company to pursue other opportunities.</p>
<p>Most recently, Reichenstein was vice president and controller of Ford Motor Co's automotive worldwide division. He spent 31 years with Ford.</p>
